Exercise 1.6

  3. I would rather have the answer to the Bayesian question because the application process is not repeated and the Bayesian question is more practical in our daily lives when I apply for a job.

Excercise 1.8

  1. Bayesian statistics can help people to ascertain a hypothesis based on the existing data, besides, with more data, the conclusion will be more clear.
  2. Both Bayesian and and frequentist statistics aim to learn from data about the world around us. Moreover, with more data, the their conclusions are more likely to become the same. And with more data, the distinguishment between bayesain and frequentists statistics is less clear.
